│ identify all instructions that are part of the VPlan or      │
│ skipped for cost computation. This leads to a false          │
│ negative, causing the assertion to fail even when the VPlan  │
│ legitimately contains additional simplifications.\n\n4.      │
│ **Proposed Edit Points**:\n   - **Edit Point 1**: Modify     │
│ `planContainsAdditionalSimplifications` to ensure it         │
